	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=173421><span id=Scholar>Quasare</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>47 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Hello :)<br>For improving an instrument skill you MUST have an instrument in your off hand while singing!<br>To improve wind and swimming, start aqua song, put a flute (or any wind instrument) in your off hand and jump in the water :)<br>To improve Brass just the same, put a brass instrument in your off hand and start DDD or fear; the best place for me to improve this skill at low lvl is to enter Arena (next to Lake Rathe) and start singing (just before lunch, bath, going out), no npc there, so no risk of agro...<br>Just remember also to put 1 point in your skills at any bard guild! (percu, wind, brass, singing and string)<br>Hope this help :)<br><br></p>&nbsp;<br>Valaba Noirac<br>Bard<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=150528" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=150528</a></td></td></tr>
