	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=classes.html?class=4&mid=102311487922314>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102311487922314>RE: Brand new Bard</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=4&mid=102311487922314#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Mon, Jun 3rd 10:45 AM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=61546><span id=Sage>Slipskin</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>1056 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.65]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>DEX is the stat that determines failure rates on starting songs.&nbsp;&nbsp;Vah Shir are not that badly off there.  In fact, my opinion is that Vah Shir have really great starting stats as bards.<br><br>Since twisting involves frequent starting and stopping of songs I would consider DEX.  Since the Vah Shir are good in that stat to begin with and it is easy to get DEX boosting gear I would not go too overboard with investing a lot of points into DEX.  STA is where Vah Shir bards hurt most.  STA translates into hit points. Since bards are the worlds biggest aggro generators consider boosting your STA a bit.  It doesn't hurt to boost CHA a little either.<br><br>When I started my Vah Shir bard I went with 5 CHA, 10 DEX, and 5 STA.<br><br>Also, on Bertoxxolus Server I have yet to see a Vah Shir bard that does not have black fur.  I had created one of the first Vah Shir bards on my server and thought I was being original (and cool). Now it seems every Vah Shir bard I have seen has black fur like mine.  So, I guess its now a class tradition to have black fur on Vah Shir bards.<br><br>Anyone out there with a Vah Shir bard that does not have black fur?</p>&nbsp;<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104222</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=479760</a></td></td></tr>
